detaileddescription.para: This means SyxOop indexes an object into the syx memory

Each known class has default instance variables used by the VM that are mandatory. These indexes are used to facilitate the access these variables and are contained in SyxObject::data

List of commands of a bytecode in SyxBytecode::code

Each type is relative to a class defined in syx-error.c
